# game/Scenes/Adrian/adrian11.rpy:14
translate portuguese adrian11_e6b6169b:

    # "Adrian and I have a little time to talk before class."
    "A Adrian e eu temos um tempinho para conversar antes da aula."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/adrian11.rpy:15
translate portuguese adrian11_584cd980:

    # pc "Haven't seen you in Souls of War as much lately. Everything okay?"
    pc "Não te tenho visto muito no Souls of War ultimamente. Está tudo bem?"

# game/Scenes/Adrian/adrian11.rpy:16
translate portuguese adrian11_c8aa5afa:

    # gg "Oh! Yeah, everything is great actually."
    gg "Oh! Sim, na verdade está tudo ótimo."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/adrian11.rpy:17
translate portuguese adrian11_93e26893:

    # gg "I've been kind of busy with this arcade idea though."
    gg "Mas tenho estado um pouco ocupado com esta ideia do salão de jogos."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/adrian11.rpy:18
translate portuguese adrian11_37a88e09:

    # gg "I talked to Gertrude, one of the school counselors, you know?"
    gg "Falei com a Gertrude, uma das orientadoras da escola, sabes?"

# game/Scenes/Adrian/adrian11.rpy:20
translate portuguese adrian11_25ef1d29:

    # pc "Oh, yeah. I know her."
    pc "Oh, sim. Conheço-a."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/adrian11.rpy:21
translate portuguese adrian11_e7b7b41e:

    # gg "She helped me change up all my classes for next semester. It's all set up now."
    gg "Ela ajudou-me a mudar todas as minhas aulas para o próximo semestre. Está tudo pronto agora."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/adrian11.rpy:22
translate portuguese adrian11_f428f0b6:

    # pc "Oh, cool!"
    pc "Oh, fixe!"

# game/Scenes/Adrian/adrian11.rpy:23
translate portuguese adrian11_f224267b:

    # gg "And in my spare time at home I've been doing a lot of research."
    gg "E no meu tempo livre em casa, tenho feito muita pesquisa."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/adrian11.rpy:24
translate portuguese adrian11_b9375b6a:

    # gg "I even wrote up a formal business plan. Want to see?"
    gg "Até redigi um plano de negócios formal. Queres ver?"

# game/Scenes/Adrian/adrian11.rpy:25
translate portuguese adrian11_61f77a4c:

    # pc "Sure."
    pc "Claro."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/adrian11.rpy:28
translate portuguese adrian11_8dfefed2:

    # "She puts a folder with typed papers in front of me, and I flip through it."
    "Ela coloca uma pasta com papéis datilografados à minha frente, e eu folheio-a."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/adrian11.rpy:29
translate portuguese adrian11_37adcdf0:

    # "There's so much information here, so much detail. She knows far more about this stuff than I do, obviously. I'm not even sure where to begin."
    "Há tanta informação aqui, tantos detalhes. Ela sabe muito mais sobre isto do que eu, obviamente. Nem sei por onde começar."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/adrian11.rpy:30
translate portuguese adrian11_6d5e4bce:

    # gg "How does it look?"
    gg "O que achas?"

# game/Scenes/Adrian/adrian11.rpy:31
translate portuguese adrian11_08f3eb16:

    # pc "I mean, I'm no expert here, but it looks great to me."
    pc "Quer dizer, não sou especialista nisto, mas a mim parece-me ótimo."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/adrian11.rpy:32
translate portuguese adrian11_f9c7e107:

    # gg "The goal is to get people to invest so that I can get some startup money."
    gg "O objetivo é conseguir que as pessoas invistam para que eu consiga algum dinheiro inicial."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/adrian11.rpy:33
translate portuguese adrian11_10293973:

    # pc "If I had the money, I'd invest for sure."
    pc "Se tivesse dinheiro, investiria com certeza."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/adrian11.rpy:36
translate portuguese adrian11_c4fb707b:

    # gg "Awesome! That makes me super happy."
    gg "Fantástico! Isso deixa-me super feliz."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/adrian11.rpy:37
translate portuguese adrian11_0c2c19e9:

    # gg "I'm actually feeling like, really good about myself right now."
    gg "Na verdade, sinto-me muito bem comigo mesma neste momento."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/adrian11.rpy:38
translate portuguese adrian11_1c658d00:

    # gg "Better than I've ever felt, maybe."
    gg "Talvez melhor do que alguma vez me senti."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/adrian11.rpy:41
translate portuguese adrian11_75dceae8:

    # gg "I feel like I'm accepted for who I am."
    gg "Sinto que sou aceite tal como sou."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/adrian11.rpy:43
translate portuguese adrian11_ae80f6d3:

    # gg "I have a pretty cool boyfriend."
    gg "Tenho um namorado muito fixe."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/adrian11.rpy:44
translate portuguese adrian11_cfc70d4a:

    # gg "And I feel like my life is heading in the right direction, for once."
    gg "E sinto que a minha vida está a seguir na direção certa, pela primeira vez."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/adrian11.rpy:45
translate portuguese adrian11_07e7c552:

    # pc "I'm really happy for you."
    pc "Estou muito feliz por ti."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/adrian11.rpy:49
translate portuguese adrian11_c7d52788:

    # gg "Thanks, [pcname]. I'm glad you're behind me."
    gg "Obrigada, [pcname]. Fico contente por me apoiares."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/adrian11.rpy:50
translate portuguese adrian11_c46a0b54:

    # pc "Any time."
    pc "Sempre à disposição."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/adrian11.rpy:53
translate portuguese adrian11_380ece13:

    # "She looks away, blushing a bit."
    "Ela desvia o olhar, corando um pouco."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/adrian11.rpy:54
translate portuguese adrian11_91c10599:

    # "Then Ms. Welch starts her lecture and we have to focus on school work."
    "Depois, a Sra. Welch começa a aula e temos de nos concentrar nos trabalhos escolares."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/adrian11.rpy:57
translate portuguese adrian11_b3da124f:

    # "The rest of the school day passes by pretty quick, then it's time for work."
    "O resto do dia letivo passa bem rápido, e depois é hora de ir trabalhar."

